title: One UI 4.1 starts rolling out to Galaxy A52 5G, Galaxy S10, Galaxy Note 10, Galaxy Z Fold 2 and Galaxy Z Flip
content:
After making its debut on the Galaxy S22 series, One UI 4.1 has slowly been making its way to more and more Galaxy phones over the past weeks. We have already seen Samsung rolling out a stable One UI 4.1 update to the Galaxy Z Fold 3, Galaxy Z Flip 3, Galaxy Note 20, and

The post One UI 4.1 starts rolling out to Galaxy A52 5G, Galaxy S10, Galaxy Note 10, Galaxy Z Fold 2 and Galaxy Z Flip appeared first on xda-developers.
description: Samsung has started rolling out a stable One UI 4.1 update to the Galaxy A52 5G, Galaxy S10, Galaxy Note 10, Galaxy Z Fold 2, and Galaxy Z Flip.
